data.description: Looking for that home with room to roam? Then come see this one that sits on 4.8 acres with mature trees. Classic style home with front porch perfect for rocking chairs and admiring the nature that surrounds you. Huge eat in kitchen and separate dining room. Family room with fireplace and formal living room. Master bedroom offers a 9 x 9 walk in closet with full master bath complete with jetted tub, separate shower and double sink. 3 additional bedrooms, laundry and 2nd full bath round out the second level of this home. The possibilities are endless with the full unfinished basement. Room for everyone inside and out!
